description:
This is a 16 minute workout called 'Stretching for Runners' from the channel Peter Donohoe.
The workout falls under Flexibility/Stretching.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Reboot Workout and The Deep Recharge vibe.
The The Reboot Workout vibe means Deep stretch, low stress, total-body refresh. This is especially good for Recovery days, stress relief, post-travel stiffness. The The Deep Recharge vibe means Nervous system reset, ultra-gentle movement. This is especially good for Times of extreme stress, fatigue, or mental overload..
The technique difficulty is Beginner and Intermediate.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: Move through both static and dynamic stretches with Peter and Aisyah, ideal for after a run. ...
